[SN]TITLE[SN]
CCTV of High Wycombe hit-and-run released

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
CCTV footage has been released of a hit-and-run showing a pedestrian being knocked down and left lying in a road.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The man was hit by a black saloon car as he crossed a road in High Wycombe.
Footage shows the car brake sharply and then speed off, with the driver apparently having "no regard for the injured man left lying in the road".
Police have appealed for the driver and witnesses who came to help the victim, aged 50, to come forward.
